    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand more on the Mill part? Like, how exactly would his ideas apply to modern things like content moderation or data privacy laws? I want to make sure the connection between classical liberty and the digital age is watertight in my post.",
      "source": "evaluator"
